data.description: Nestled in the heart of the highly sought-after Arrowhead Ranch community, this exquisite 4 bedroom, 2 bath home on a spacious corner lot is a true gem. With its resort-style amenities and modern upgrades, it's the perfect blend of comfort, style, and luxury. 4 Bedrooms, say goodbye to cramped spaces! This home offers ample room for your family, guests, or even a home office. 2 Bathrooms, enjoy updated bathrooms that exude sophistication and relaxation. Gourmet Kitchen: Prepare meals with ease in your kitchen featuring beautiful granite countertops, ample cabinet space, and modern appliances. Spacious Living Areas: Entertain guests or unwind with family in the generously sized living room and dining area. Picture-Perfect Outdoor Space! Don't miss out!
